rwg rwmklI iv`c gurU Amrdws jI dI bwxI 'AnMd'[
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
hy BweI mW! (myry AMdr) pUrn iKVwau pYdw ho igAw hY (ikauNik) mYnUM gurU iml ipAw hY[
mYnUM gurU imilAw hY, qy nwl hI Afol AvsQw BI pRwpq ho geI hY (Bwv, gurU dy imlx nwl myrw mn folxoN ht igAw hY); myry mn ivc (mwno) ^uSI dy vwjy v`j pey hn,
sohxy rwg Awpxy prvwr qy rwxIAW smyq (myry mn ivc, mwno,) pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dy gIq gwvx Aw gey hn[
(qusI BI) pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dw gIq gwvo[ ijn@W ijn@W ny is&q-swlwh dw Sbd mn ivc vswieAw hY (auhnW dy AMdr pUrn iKVwau pYdw ho jWdw hY)[
nwnk AwKdw hY (myry AMdr BI) AwnMd bx igAw hY (ikauNik) mYnUM siqgurU iml ipAw hY ]1]
hy myry mn! qUM sdw pRBU dy nwl (juiVAw) rhu[
hy myry mn! qUM sdw pRBU nUM Xwd r`K[
auh pRBU swry du`K dUr krn vwlw hY[
auh sdw qyrI shwieqw krn vwlw hY qyry swry kMm isry cwVHn dy smr`Q hY[
aus mwlk nUM ikauN (Awpxy) mn qoN BulWdw hYN jo swry kMm krn-jogw hY? nwnk AwKdw hY ik hy myry mn! qUM sdw pRBU dy crnW ivc juiVAw rhu ]2]
hy sdw kwiem rihx vwly mwlk (-pRBU)! (mYN qyry dr qoN mn dw AwnMd mMgdw hW, pr) qyry Gr ivc kyhVI cIz nhIN hY?
qyry Gr ivc qW hryk cIz mOjUd hY, auhI mnu`K pRwpq krdw hY ijs nUM qUM Awp dyNdw hYN[
(iPr, auh mnu`K) qyrw nwm qy qyrI is&q-swlwh (Awpxy) mn ivc vsWdw hY (ijs dI brkiq nwl aus dy AMdr AwnMd pYdw ho jWdw hY)[
ijn@W bMidAW dy mn ivc (qyrw) nwm v`sdw hY (auhnW dy AMdr, mwno,) byAMq swzW dIAW (imlvIAW) surW v`jx l`g pYNdIAW hn (Bwv, auhnW dy mn ivc auh ^uSI qy cwau pYdw huMdw hY jo keI swzW dw imlvW rwg sux ky pYdw huMdw hY)[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik hy sdw kwiem rihx vwly mwlk! qyry Gr ivc iksy SY dw Gwtw nhIN hY (qy, mYN qyry dr qoN AwnMd dw dwn mMgdw hW) ]3]
(pRBU dI myhr nwl aus dw) sdw-iQr rihx vwlw nwm myrI izMdgI dw Awsrw (bx igAw) hY[
auh sdw kwiem rihx vwlw nwm myrI izMdgI dw Awsrw bx igAw) hY, ijs (hir-nwm) ny myry swry lwlc dUr kr id`qy hn[
jo hir-nwm (myry AMdr) SWqI qy suK pYdw krky myry mn ivc Aw itikAw hY, ijs (hir-nwm) ny myry mn dIAW swrIAW kwmnW pUrIAW kr id`qIAW hn[
mYN (Awpxy Awp nUM) Awpxy gurU qoN sdky krdw hW, ikauNik ieh swrIAW brkqW gurU dIAW hI hn[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik hy sMq jno! (gurU dw Sbd) suxo, gurU dy Sbd ivc ipAwr bxwE[
(siqgurU dI myhr nwl hI pRBU dw) sdw kwiem rihx vwlw nwm myrI izMdgI dw Awsrw (bx igAw) hY ]4]
aus BwgW vwly (ihrdy-) Gr ivc (mwno) pMj iksmW dy swzW dIAW imlvIAW surW v`j pYNdIAW hn,
ijs (ihrdy-) Gr ivc (hy pRBU! qUM) s`iqAw pweI hY, aus BwgW vwly (ihrdy-) Gr ivc (mwno) pMj iksmW dy swzW dIAW imlvIAW surW v`j pYNdIAW hn (Bwv, aus ihrdy ivc pUrn AwnMd bx jWdw hY),
(hy pRBU!) aus dy pMjy kwmwidk vYrI qUM kwbU ivc kr dyNdw hYN, qy frwx vwlw kwl (Bwv, mOq dw fr) dUr kr dyNdw hYN[
pr isr& auhI mnu`K hir-nwm ivc juVdy hn ijn@W dy BwgW ivc qUM Dur qoN hI AwpxI myhr nwl (ismrn dw lyK ilK ky) r`K id`qw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik aus ihrdy-Gr ivc suK pYdw huMdw hY, aus ihrdy ivc (mwno) iek-rs (vwjy) v`jdy hn ]5]
sdw-iQr pRBU dy crnW dI lgn (dy AwnMd) qoN ibnw ieh (mnu`Kw) srIr inAwsrw jyhw hI rihMdw hY[
pRBU-crnW dI pRIq qoN ibnw inAwsrw hoieAw hoieAw ieh srIr jo kuJ BI krdw hY nkwry kMm hI krdw hY[
hy jgq dy mwlk! qUM hI ikrpw kr! (qw ik ieh gurU dy Sbd ivc l`g ky suDr jwey) koeI hor ies nUM suc`jy pwsy lwx jogw hI nhIN[
qYQoN ibnw koeI hor QW nhIN ijQy ieh srIr suc`jy pwsy l`g sky[ (qyrI ikRpw nwl hI) ieh gurU dy Sbd ivc l`g ky suDr skdw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik pRBU-crnW dI pRIq qoN ibnw ieh srIr pr-ADIn (Bwv, mwieAw dy pRBwv hyT) hY qy jo kuJ krdw hY inkMmw kMm hI krdw hY ]6]
AwKx nUM qW hr koeI AwK dyNdw hY ik mYnUM AwnMd pRwpq ho igAw hY, pr (Asl) AwnMd dI sUJ gurU qoN hI imldI hY[
hy ipAwry BweI! (Asl) AwnMd dI sUJ sdw gurU qoN hI imldI hY[ (auh mnu`K Asl AwnMd nwl sWJ pWdw hY, ijs auqy gurU) ikrpw krdw hY[
gurU myhr kr ky (aus dy) (AMdroN) pwp k`t dyNdw hY, qy (aus dIAW ivcwr-A`KW ivc) Awqmk jIvn dI sUJ dw surmw pWdw hY[
ijn@W mnu`KW dy mn ivcoN mwieAw dw moh mu`k jWdw hY, Akwl purK auhnW dw bol hI suc`jw im`Tw kr dyNdw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik Asl AwnMd iehI hY, qy ieh AwnMd gurU qoN hI smiJAw jw skdw hY ]7]
